Description: Time and weather announcement system for Asterisk
 Announces the current time and weather conditions through
 Asterisk. Supports 12/24 hour time formats, multiple
 timezones, and weather information from various sources.
 Designed for use with radio systems and repeater controllers.
 .
 Features include:
  * Time announcements in 12/24 hour format
  * Weather conditions from multiple data sources
  * Support for international airport codes
  * Configurable caching system
  * Comprehensive logging
  * Custom sound directory support 